OL,5, A close government ally of Italy's     
OL,6, Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni has      
OL,7, attracted claims of white supremacy for
OL,8, saying Italians are at risk of "ethnic 
OL,9, replacement".                          
OL,11,FAgriculture Minister Francesco         
OL,12,FLollobrigida said: "Italians are having
OL,13,Ffewer children, so we're replacing them
OL,14,Fwith someone else."                    
OL,16,F"That's not the way forward," he added.
OL,18,FMr Lollobrigida is from the same       
OL,19,Ffar-right party as Ms Meloni and he is 
OL,20,Falso her brother-in law.               
